Frieda Rosinski, Appellee, v. Metropolitan Life Insurance Company, Appellant.Gen. No. 40,633.

(Abstract of Decision.)

Heard in second division, first district, this court at April term, 1939;opinion filed May 28, 1940.Hoyne, O’Connor & Rubinkam, for appellant; Nathaniel Rubinkam and Ira W. Hurley, of counsel; Ewart Harris, for appellee. Opinion by Justice Scanlan.

“Not to be published in full.”
